name: Pours Of Melanin
description: This is my 2nd canvas paint pour + GAN collage. The canvas painting I made in 2020 I based on my old modeling shoot photograph from 2006 and mixed with inspirational words that I felt described myself and my beautiful friend I created this for. I wanted to see what it was like to run the photograph of the canvas through deep dream. The result was stunning! I hope you enjoy!!
